    <title>Laravel的安装</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/07/18/1.%20Laravel%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/07/18/1.%20Laravel%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/</id>
    <published>2022-07-18T03:04:19.566Z</published>
    <updated>2022-07-18T03:07:36.901Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Laravel的安装"><a href="#Laravel的安装" class="headerlink" title="Laravel的安装"></a>Laravel的安装</h1><p>[^* 前提：安装了PHP study套件 *]: </p><hr><h5 id="一、安装composer"><a href="#一、安装composer" class="headerlink" title="一、安装composer"></a>一、安装composer</h5><p>下载地址：<a href="http://getcomposer.org/Composer-Setup.exe">composer安装</a>🛒</p><hr><h5 id="二、配置镜像"><a href="#二、配置镜像" class="headerlink" title="二、配置镜像"></a>二、配置镜像</h5><p><em>命令提示符输入：</em></p><p>➡**<code>composer config -g repo.packagist composer https://mirrors.aliyun.com/composer/</code>**</p><hr><h5 id="三、安装Laravel项目"><a href="#三、安装Laravel项目" class="headerlink" title="三、安装Laravel项目"></a>三、安装Laravel项目</h5><p><em>命令提示符输入：</em></p><p>➡**<code>composer create-project --prefer-dist laravel/Laravel=6 D:\Laravel</code>**</p><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">命令含义：</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span>. composer</span><br><span class="line">#执行composer</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2</span>. create-project</span><br><span class="line">#创建项目</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3</span>. laravel/laravel</span><br><span class="line">#创建Laravel项目，默认为最新版本 （可在后加“=x”指定版本，x代表版本号）</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">4</span>. --prefer-dist</span><br><span class="line">#强制使用压缩包的方式下载    节省时间</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">5</span>. D:\Laravel</span><br><span class="line">#创建路径   （确保路径目录为空）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="/2022/07/18/1.%20Laravel%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/note\img\image-20220718102223268.png" alt="image-20220718102223268" style="zoom:150%;"><hr><h5 id="四、启动Laravel框架"><a href="#四、启动Laravel框架" class="headerlink" title="四、启动Laravel框架"></a>四、启动Laravel框架</h5><ol><li><p>打开PHP study面板，<u>网站</u>一栏点击<u>创建网站</u></p></li><li><p>编辑<u>基本配置</u>，域名格式为:”##.##”,根目录选择刚刚安装好的Laravel项目下的<u>public</u>文件夹。 eg：baidu.com</p><img src="/2022/07/18/1.%20Laravel%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/source\images\1. Laravel安装\image-20220718110123376.png" alt="image-20220718110123376" style="zoom: 80%;"></li><li><p>编辑路径下”<strong>nginx.htaccess</strong>“文件</p><p>输入以下代码：</p><blockquote><p>location &#x2F; {<br>      # First attempt to serve request as file, then<br>      # as directory, then fall back to displaying a 404.<br>      # try_files $uri $uri&#x2F; &#x3D;404;<br>​                try_files $uri $uri&#x2F; &#x2F;index.php?$query_string;<br>}</p></blockquote></li><li><p>浏览器访问设置好的<strong>域名</strong>，就可以进入Laravel项目的原始页面了。</p></li></ol><img src="/2022/07/18/1.%20Laravel%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/source\images\1. Laravel安装\image-20220718110154286.png" alt="image-20220718110154286" style="zoom:80%;">]]></content>
    
    
      
      
